{"tid":714862,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"日本仔對於sony xz2 睇法","createTime":"2018-06-24T03:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T12:11:16.000Z","uid":141060,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8c954b17e636e63a44165b0b667bcc0ba64cf937","tid":714862,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:46:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kuronekoblog.com/47761/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkuronekoblog.com%2F47761%2F&d=qGEn258Ii1sbyQSJeHwt0TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=24b966bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kuronekoblog.com/47761/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://kuronekoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/20180623_225152_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkuronekoblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F20180623_225152_1.gif&h=b5ccd4b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xperia XZ2/XZ2 Compact」のデザインは分厚くてダサい？実際に使ってみた感想<br />\n投稿日：2018年6月24日<br />\n<br />\n「Xperia XZ2」と「Xperia XZ2 Compact」のデザインの評価が悪くて話題になっていますね。<br />\n<br />\n「Xperia XZ2」は現在売り上げが絶不調となっていて、発売日の週は売上ランキング上位に入ったものの、2週目には前作「Xperia XZ1」に販売台数で負けてしまい、悪い意味で注目されてしまいました。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">この売上結果になってしまった背景には、評判の悪かったデザインが強く影響していると思われますが、今回はそんな「Xperia XZ2/XZ2 Compact」のデザインについて解説していきたいと思います。</span><br />\n<br />\n大意係柒設計嚴重影響銷量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eeb4607587f8e3a1c7723e0f7099fb587a5af0a","tid":714862,"uid":49664,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://kuronekoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/20180623_225152_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fkuronekoblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F20180623_225152_1.gif&h=3b5ce1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://kuronekoblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/20180623_225152_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fkuronekoblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F20180623_225152_1.gif&h=3b5ce1cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2943482f0d2c9253825cf58474d9a25c7fed934","tid":714862,"uid":100873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"以前用neo V覺得可以咁轉好過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a059af8c49b61ce8c28d8650bb504e7c081af4","tid":714862,"uid":92477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/115854_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F115854_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=19096fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a540c328ad50dfd8d764b42e6654228e18ce7ffd","tid":714862,"uid":191812,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/121957_5f76448058d9651e69d37ca6eab7b3d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F121957_5f76448058d9651e69d37ca6eab7b3d8.jpg&h=af5511f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗起以前部x8"},{"pid":"866083f3393fd7f3abbe07b4459e654e2d77f9c9","tid":714862,"uid":163758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:24:37.000Z","msg":"wfc<br />\n日狗係咪都係買iphone"},{"pid":"55fb7d3166f7d1ef77df9596aeb1dc3fa4fe680c","tid":714862,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"根本冇請設計師好耐. 冇心去攪. <br />\n以前用 ARC S 日系機好靚. 果個年代出好多新